Luanco.title: Luanco
Luanco.byline: The fishing village of Luanco is a coastal town, with a beach, in Asturias province in northern Spain.

Luang Namtha.title: Luang Namtha
Luang Namtha.byline: Luang Namtha (ຫຼວງນໍ້າທາ, ຫລວງນໍ້າທາ Louangnamtha, Luang Nam Tha) is the largest city in Luang Nam Tha Province, Northern Laos.

Luang Prabang.title: Luang Prabang
Luang Prabang.byline: Luang Prabang (Lao: ຫຼວງພຣະບາງ, pronounced Loo-ang pah-bang and also spelled Louangphrabang, is the former capital of Laos and a UNESCO World Heritage city.

Luanchuan.title: Luanchuan
Luanchuan.byline: Luanchuan County (栾川县) is a county under the jurisdiction of Luoyang, Henan Province, China.
